This is a bug. I want to paste preformatted text into Confluence that looks something like this:

{noformat}
#define foo         12345
#define jabberwocky 67890
{noformat}

and no matter what I try, Confluence coalesces the whitespace into a single space:

{noformat}
#define foo 12345
#define jabberwocky 67890
{noformat}

Please either fix this to paste exactly what is in the clipboard, or provide a mechanism by which the content of the clipboard can be pasted verbatim.
